            <title>[SOLR-12728] RequestLoggingTest fails on occasion, not reproducible</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-12728</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m getting about a 1.5% failure rate in RequestLoggingTest, I strongly suspect it&apos;s a result of the async logging changed from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-12055&quot; title=&quot;Enable async logging by default&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-12055&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-12055&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, digging...&lt;/p&gt;

